Daniel Caldwell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Caldwell 0 Daniel Edmund Caldwell (1935 – March 15, 2015) was an American actor, stage director and drama teacher. He was the founder of Conservatory Theatre Ensemble in Mill Valley, California, where he taught drama at Tamalpais High School.
